3
00:00:11,262 --> 00:00:13,531
Starting with Silla, I will behead Go Geon...

4
00:00:13,531 --> 00:00:15,626
and then unify the three nations!

5
00:00:16,432 --> 00:00:18,367
The man just right for the job...

6
00:00:18,371 --> 00:00:20,837
is your husband, General On.

7
00:00:21,001 --> 00:00:23,436
Go to him and persuade him.

8
00:00:23,542 --> 00:00:25,637
Whichever mountain you hide yourself in,

9
00:00:27,341 --> 00:00:28,837
I am going to find you.

10
00:00:29,152 --> 00:00:30,407
You will fail...

11
00:00:30,812 --> 00:00:32,351
because I will make sure no one finds me.

12
00:00:32,352 --> 00:00:34,877
An envoy came from Silla, and he is...

13
00:00:35,051 --> 00:00:37,051
An envoy from Silla?

14
00:00:37,051 --> 00:00:39,387
Are you not the traitor Go Geon?

15
00:00:41,521 --> 00:00:44,756
Are you here to die in your own land?

16
00:00:45,161 --> 00:00:46,932
(Episode 19)

17
00:00:46,932 --> 00:00:48,597
I came to see you, Your Highness.

18
00:00:49,731 --> 00:00:52,326
I thought it would be more meaningful...

19
00:00:52,602 --> 00:00:54,766
to see you one last time...

20
00:00:55,472 --> 00:00:56,766
than to live a meaningless life in Silla.

21
00:00:59,811 --> 00:01:01,877
Your plan will never go your way...

22
00:01:03,012 --> 00:01:04,777
as the King...

23
00:01:05,081 --> 00:01:07,716
plans to send back the envoys.

24
00:01:10,121 --> 00:01:11,947
I want to ask you one more thing.

25
00:01:13,091 --> 00:01:14,257
That night...

26
00:01:17,591 --> 00:01:19,497
Was it your sword?

27
00:01:21,602 --> 00:01:23,867
That stabbed my father?

28
00:01:37,111 --> 00:01:38,206
That is right.

29
00:01:41,121 --> 00:01:42,587
Just like how your father...

30
00:01:43,822 --> 00:01:45,986
shot an arrow at my mother.

31
00:01:53,361 --> 00:01:54,956
It should end with that night.

32
00:01:55,331 --> 00:01:59,197
The resentment and ill fates should end with us.

33
00:01:59,572 --> 00:02:01,197
Princess, the ill fates...

34
00:02:02,242 --> 00:02:04,307
could have ended long ago.

35
00:02:04,512 --> 00:02:07,137
If the two families came together through a royal wedding,

36
00:02:09,382 --> 00:02:12,076
you and I would have changed this empire.

37
00:02:12,111 --> 00:02:13,276
Not at all.

38
00:02:14,981 --> 00:02:16,546
It would have become the world...

39
00:02:17,192 --> 00:02:19,287
of the Gyeru Tribe that Gochuga dreamed of.

40
00:02:20,792 --> 00:02:22,887
Go back to Silla.

41
00:02:23,231 --> 00:02:24,956
And forget all of your memories from here.

42
00:02:26,331 --> 00:02:28,456
There is a woman who only loves you.

43
00:02:30,271 --> 00:02:32,996
I am here to die. I want to die...

44
00:02:34,042 --> 00:02:36,107
to end our ill fate.

45
00:02:37,812 --> 00:02:39,206
Please stop.

46
00:02:39,681 --> 00:02:40,740
Leave.

47
00:02:40,741 --> 00:02:42,137
I will not.

48
00:02:42,782 --> 00:02:44,676
- What? - Because...

49
00:02:46,122 --> 00:02:48,746
I followed you to save you.

50
00:02:50,692 --> 00:02:52,347
Return safely, Master Go.

51
00:02:53,461 --> 00:02:54,956
I will not see you out.

52
00:03:12,042 --> 00:03:14,306
You asked to see me at such a late hour.

53
00:03:14,882 --> 00:03:16,046
What is this?

54
00:03:16,211 --> 00:03:18,676
As the leader of the Five Tribe council,

55
00:03:18,912 --> 00:03:20,016
I came here...

56
00:03:20,521 --> 00:03:24,486
to tell you that Go Geon must not be allowed to live.

57
00:03:24,622 --> 00:03:26,717
What is this arrow for?

58
00:03:32,032 --> 00:03:35,056
When I went to confiscate Gyeru Tribe's assets,

59
00:03:35,562 --> 00:03:37,866
I happened to find it.

60
00:03:41,572 --> 00:03:43,667
Go Won Pyo's servant...

61
00:03:44,042 --> 00:03:46,576
told me the story behind this arrow.

62
00:03:49,551 --> 00:03:53,021
This is the arrow that was used to kill...

63
00:03:53,021 --> 00:03:54,847
Queen Yeon, your mother.

64
00:03:55,021 --> 00:03:56,917
It is that very arrow.

65
00:03:58,322 --> 00:03:59,717
Go Won Pyo.

66
00:04:00,762 --> 00:04:05,127
He seems to have kept it like a trophy.

67
00:04:06,301 --> 00:04:10,526
Will you still let that man's son live?

68
00:04:35,721 --> 00:04:37,986
Oh my, Princess.

69
00:04:38,831 --> 00:04:41,926
Gwanno Tribe's Lord Jin went to see the King.

70
00:04:43,401 --> 00:04:45,271
What for? At this late hour?

71
00:04:45,271 --> 00:04:46,897
I do not know that,

72
00:04:47,242 --> 00:04:50,566
but the King just summoned his bodyguards.

73
00:04:57,012 --> 00:04:59,681
Master Go, you must get away.

74
00:04:59,682 --> 00:05:00,777
Why?

75
00:05:01,682 --> 00:05:03,951
Did the King decide to kill me?

76
00:05:03,951 --> 00:05:05,546
Yes, he will.

77
00:05:05,922 --> 00:05:07,517
So you must get away.

78
00:05:08,922 --> 00:05:11,056
If I act as kindling.

79
00:05:12,432 --> 00:05:14,357
Goguryeo will go down in flames.

80
00:05:15,562 --> 00:05:17,132
I came here expecting that.

81
00:05:17,132 --> 00:05:19,401
Bring your own men and fight.

82
00:05:19,401 --> 00:05:21,502
Do not die a pointless death.

83
00:05:21,502 --> 00:05:23,866
If you want to avenge your father, do so properly.

84
00:05:24,672 --> 00:05:26,736
If you return as a commander,

85
00:05:27,041 --> 00:05:28,707
then I will take you on.

86
00:05:33,922 --> 00:05:35,577
We are going to the library.

87
00:05:35,882 --> 00:05:38,252
We must find some diplomatic papers.

88
00:05:38,252 --> 00:05:39,791
The envoys cannot leave.

89
00:05:39,791 --> 00:05:42,287
Are you stopping me because you do not know who I am?

90
00:05:42,992 --> 00:05:44,426
If you do not believe me,

91
00:05:44,891 --> 00:05:45,986
come with us.

92
00:06:07,552 --> 00:06:08,647
Follow me.

93
00:06:24,701 --> 00:06:26,537
The envoys disappeared!

94
00:06:26,572 --> 00:06:27,796
Search thoroughly!

95
00:06:29,172 --> 00:06:30,267
Find them!

96
00:06:37,711 --> 00:06:40,077
This could put the Princess in danger.

97
00:06:40,622 --> 00:06:44,116
Would you rather turn back now?

98
00:06:46,091 --> 00:06:47,186
No.

99
00:06:49,291 --> 00:06:51,287
She bruised my ego.

100
00:06:52,262 --> 00:06:53,857
I must return the favor.

101
00:06:54,002 --> 00:06:56,296
What did you two talk about?

102
00:06:56,771 --> 00:06:57,866
Or was it...

103
00:06:59,372 --> 00:07:01,496
a sweet conversation that you had wanted?

104
00:07:04,141 --> 00:07:06,006
The main roads will be searched.

105
00:07:06,411 --> 00:07:08,277
Horses will do us no good.

106
00:07:08,682 --> 00:07:11,777
We will have to walk to the border. Can you manage?

107
00:07:12,252 --> 00:07:14,847
We will not be safe even in Silla.

108
00:07:16,192 --> 00:07:18,546
The established authority...

109
00:07:18,922 --> 00:07:20,657
will not look upon us with favor.

110
00:07:20,992 --> 00:07:22,417
We must get out of here first.

111
00:07:24,791 --> 00:07:26,327
Where is Go Geon?

112
00:07:32,271 --> 00:07:33,897
I asked you where he is.

113
00:07:35,672 --> 00:07:38,936
I helped him escape.

114
00:07:39,312 --> 00:07:40,407
What?

115
00:07:41,882 --> 00:07:43,876
He will have left the palace by now...

116
00:07:44,211 --> 00:07:45,876
and hid himself.

117
00:08:00,461 --> 00:08:03,796
Send soldiers to go after him!

118
00:08:04,502 --> 00:08:07,236
Also, arrest the Princess.

119
00:08:07,601 --> 00:08:08,696
Your Majesty.

120
00:08:09,172 --> 00:08:10,467
You heard me.

121
00:08:10,641 --> 00:08:13,277
Arrest her and throw her in prison!

122
00:08:13,742 --> 00:08:14,837
- Yes, sire. - Yes, sire.

123
00:08:16,081 --> 00:08:17,176
Let me go.

124
00:08:18,312 --> 00:08:19,917
I will go myself.

125
00:08:33,462 --> 00:08:34,626
Your Majesty.

126
00:08:35,602 --> 00:08:37,671
Your Majesty! Please calm down.

127
00:08:37,671 --> 00:08:38,996
Shut your mouth!

128
00:08:47,112 --> 00:08:48,207
Walk!

129
00:08:50,551 --> 00:08:51,707
Get down!

130
00:08:52,612 --> 00:08:53,717
Let go!

131
00:08:55,882 --> 00:08:57,587
You must hold back.

132
00:08:58,352 --> 00:08:59,687
You fools!

133
00:09:01,762 --> 00:09:04,187
Do you know who you have tied up?

134
00:09:04,661 --> 00:09:07,602
We were ordered to bring in everyone from the Sunno Tribe.

135
00:09:07,602 --> 00:09:10,472
What? That is just nonsense!

136
00:09:10,472 --> 00:09:11,801
Release them.

137
00:09:11,801 --> 00:09:12,896
Lord Yeon.

138
00:09:12,941 --> 00:09:14,901
This is nonsense.

139
00:09:14,901 --> 00:09:16,541
Treason?

140
00:09:16,541 --> 00:09:19,006
Our tribe has been through this before.

141
00:09:20,112 --> 00:09:22,536
We will not repeat it.

142
00:09:22,882 --> 00:09:26,051
So tell your men to stand down.

143
00:09:26,051 --> 00:09:27,622
But the Princess and Lord Sa...

144
00:09:27,622 --> 00:09:29,616
If we cause a fuss here,

145
00:09:30,092 --> 00:09:32,386
it will only put the Princess at risk.

146
00:09:43,202 --> 00:09:44,626
Did you catch Go Geon?

147
00:09:46,232 --> 00:09:48,036
We cannot trace him.

148
00:09:51,641 --> 00:09:53,177
You failed to get him?

149
00:09:56,141 --> 00:09:59,207
That news just ruined my appetite.

150
00:10:00,521 --> 00:10:01,616
Your Majesty.

151
00:10:05,452 --> 00:10:09,286
Do you truly believe the Princess plotted treason?

152
00:10:09,962 --> 00:10:12,486
Is that why you ordered the Sunno Tribe to be brought in?

153
00:10:14,232 --> 00:10:17,067
You have served since my father's reign, so you must know.

154
00:10:17,301 --> 00:10:18,526
My sister...

155
00:10:19,801 --> 00:10:22,536
had never hidden her ambition to become the ruler.

156
00:10:22,641 --> 00:10:24,136
That is not true.

157
00:10:24,411 --> 00:10:26,512
She only did what she could for the royal family...

158
00:10:26,512 --> 00:10:28,177
I do not care what she thinks.

159
00:10:29,281 --> 00:10:32,146
As King, I decide whether she is a traitor or not.

160
00:10:32,852 --> 00:10:36,246
She helped Go Geon escape and that made things clear.

161
00:10:36,551 --> 00:10:39,447
Your father also made the same mistake.

162
00:10:40,592 --> 00:10:43,857
He chose to doubt rather than to believe.

163
00:10:45,632 --> 00:10:48,996
I beg you to not repeat that tragedy.

164
00:10:49,161 --> 00:10:51,227
That hangs on the Princess' decision.

165
00:10:53,002 --> 00:10:55,141
- Get in there! - Move it.

166
00:10:55,141 --> 00:10:56,771
- Lord Sa! - Move!

167
00:10:56,771 --> 00:10:57,866
Stop!

168
00:10:59,941 --> 00:11:01,437
I apologize.

169
00:11:01,941 --> 00:11:05,252
I lacked judgment and got you in trouble.

170
00:11:05,252 --> 00:11:07,016
Why are you here as well?

171
00:11:07,821 --> 00:11:09,916
General Sa. Jin.

172
00:11:09,992 --> 00:11:11,187
Princess.

173
00:11:11,921 --> 00:11:14,156
Since you first came to Ghost Valley,

174
00:11:14,862 --> 00:11:17,327
