177
00:11:23,832 --> 00:11:25,972
- Move! - Walk ahead.

178
00:11:25,972 --> 00:11:28,271
- Move along! - They say that right prevails.

179
00:11:28,271 --> 00:11:29,571
It will all work out.

180
00:11:29,571 --> 00:11:31,036
Do not worry, Ga Jin.

181
00:11:35,641 --> 00:11:38,077
- Princess! Do not do this! - Princess.

182
00:11:38,151 --> 00:11:39,882
I must see the King!

183
00:11:39,882 --> 00:11:41,276
Send word!

184
00:11:41,882 --> 00:11:43,047
Go, now!

185
00:11:48,521 --> 00:11:52,427
Release the Sunno Tribe chief and the warriors.

186
00:11:54,262 --> 00:11:55,396
If I do,

187
00:11:56,771 --> 00:11:59,827
they will side with you and threaten me.

188
00:12:00,141 --> 00:12:02,067
That will not happen.

189
00:12:02,202 --> 00:12:03,307
Then...

190
00:12:07,911 --> 00:12:09,876
prove your loyalty.

191
00:12:13,012 --> 00:12:16,077
Silla took Adan Fortress from us during our father's reign.

192
00:12:16,592 --> 00:12:18,547
I want to recover that key point.

193
00:12:20,762 --> 00:12:23,457
Get General On to take it back.

194
00:12:23,762 --> 00:12:25,656
I already told you.

195
00:12:27,401 --> 00:12:31,567
General On will not fight again.

196
00:12:34,171 --> 00:12:35,266
Then...

197
00:12:36,712 --> 00:12:38,467
why did you go to see him?

198
00:12:40,541 --> 00:12:42,707
You went to his hiding place.

199
00:12:45,181 --> 00:12:46,882
What did you talk about?

200
00:12:46,882 --> 00:12:49,847
How do you know that?

201
00:12:50,092 --> 00:12:52,416
Did you ask him to fight with you?

202
00:12:54,791 --> 00:12:57,031
To help you oust the young, lacking King,

203
00:12:57,031 --> 00:12:59,057
so you could take over?

204
00:13:03,271 --> 00:13:04,366
Won.

205
00:13:10,141 --> 00:13:11,366
If you feel wronged,

206
00:13:12,911 --> 00:13:15,136
show your loyalty.

207
00:13:33,901 --> 00:13:35,097
I would rather...

208
00:13:38,202 --> 00:13:39,766
you kill me.

209
00:13:42,141 --> 00:13:43,607
