211
00:14:05,561 --> 00:14:07,557
I understand.

212
00:14:27,122 --> 00:14:28,977
What did I tell you?

213
00:14:29,352 --> 00:14:31,317
She will not listen.

214
00:14:34,722 --> 00:14:36,656
I am tired. Please leave.

215
00:14:39,531 --> 00:14:41,597
What will you do about General On?

216
00:14:42,301 --> 00:14:44,297
He may live as a hermit now,

217
00:14:44,771 --> 00:14:46,427
