236
00:15:47,502 --> 00:15:49,457
To avoid going against the King,

237
00:15:50,602 --> 00:15:52,702
she said she would take the blame.

238
00:15:52,702 --> 00:15:55,766
Then what will happen to her?

239
00:15:57,742 --> 00:15:59,036
Lord Sa.

240
00:16:01,781 --> 00:16:03,506
The King ordered...

241
00:16:07,252 --> 00:16:09,016
she be beheaded.

242
00:16:13,992 --> 00:16:16,957
