253
00:16:48,021 --> 00:16:49,187
What?

254
00:16:49,862 --> 00:16:52,057
His actions do not follow his words?

255
00:16:52,832 --> 00:16:53,927
Yes.

256
00:16:55,362 --> 00:16:56,896
Lord Kim...

257
00:16:59,872 --> 00:17:02,297
sent this woman as a spy...

258
00:17:03,202 --> 00:17:05,271
and traveled to Goguryeo many times.

259
00:17:05,271 --> 00:17:09,037
Each time, he took valuable jewels, silver,

260
00:17:10,652 --> 00:17:12,777
and even Goguryeo women.

261
00:17:14,081 --> 00:17:15,847
For his personal gain.

262
00:17:16,551 --> 00:17:18,487
