263
00:17:19,152 --> 00:17:20,787
did you fill your own pockets?

264
00:17:21,561 --> 00:17:22,692
That is not true.

265
00:17:22,692 --> 00:17:25,226
He said the riches were for the King.

266
00:17:25,331 --> 00:17:27,226
