268
00:17:30,002 --> 00:17:31,531
Once a thief...

269
00:17:31,531 --> 00:17:33,472
is forever a thief, Your Majesty.

270
00:17:33,472 --> 00:17:36,202
I asked around myself.

271
00:17:36,202 --> 00:17:38,837
I was able to confirm that...

272
00:17:39,041 --> 00:17:42,581
whenever he visited Baekje, he took riches for his own gain.

273
00:17:42,581 --> 00:17:44,012
Even from Baekje?

274
00:17:44,012 --> 00:17:47,621
I took in you Goguryeo stragglers...

275
00:17:47,621 --> 00:17:50,652
and now you are stabbing me in the back?

276
