277
00:17:53,392 --> 00:17:55,487
he puts his livelihood first.

278
00:17:56,361 --> 00:17:57,926
You must not keep him close.

279
00:17:59,591 --> 00:18:01,097
Do not believe them.

280
00:18:01,402 --> 00:18:02,497
This is a trap.

281
00:18:03,002 --> 00:18:05,126
I am bring framed.

282
00:18:05,232 --> 00:18:07,497
We will see about that.

283
00:18:13,111 --> 00:18:15,012
- Drag him outside. - Yes, sire!

284
00:18:15,012 --> 00:18:16,436
You cannot do this.

285
00:18:16,541 --> 00:18:18,452
Your Majesty, I am innocent.

286
00:18:18,452 --> 00:18:20,277
I am innocent!

287
00:18:24,152 --> 00:18:26,047
Leave us.

288
00:18:34,131 --> 00:18:35,626
Kim Cha Seung...

289
00:18:36,361 --> 00:18:40,067
will be punished for whatever crimes he committed.

290
00:18:41,101 --> 00:18:42,267
How will you...

291
00:18:42,942 --> 00:18:46,166
pay for failing to do your duty...

292
00:18:46,942 --> 00:18:48,537
as my envoy?

293
00:18:51,982 --> 00:18:53,307
Give me...

294
00:18:56,682 --> 00:18:58,747
10,000 of your men.

295
00:19:00,422 --> 00:19:02,186
I will attack Goguryeo...

296
00:19:03,091 --> 00:19:05,186
and expand Silla's territory.

297
00:19:11,371 --> 00:19:12,827
How can I...

298
00:19:13,131 --> 00:19:15,837
entrust you with 10,000 of my soldiers?

299
00:19:21,081 --> 00:19:23,476
I saw for myself that...

300
00:19:23,912 --> 00:19:28,146
Goguryeo does not have a commander to defend their land.

301
00:19:28,321 --> 00:19:30,017
They only have paper tigers...

302
00:19:30,521 --> 00:19:32,247
who are sick and old.

303
00:19:33,861 --> 00:19:35,386
I heard that...

304
00:19:35,591 --> 00:19:39,386
Princess Pyeonggang managed to fight off Baekje's attack.

305
00:19:41,531 --> 00:19:43,626
King Yeongyang is jealous of his sister,

306
00:19:45,031 --> 00:19:46,866
so he has her locked up.

307
00:19:47,571 --> 00:19:49,166
Now is the right time.

308
00:19:49,972 --> 00:19:52,166
If you give me 10,000 men,

309
00:19:52,912 --> 00:19:54,307
I will turn Goguryeo land...

310
00:19:55,281 --> 00:19:57,646
into Silla.

311
00:20:02,621 --> 00:20:04,916
How about 30,000 men?

312
00:20:10,331 --> 00:20:14,557
To take Pyeongyang Castle as well,

313
00:20:15,162 --> 00:20:17,997
I think you will need at least 30,000 soldiers.

314
00:20:19,932 --> 00:20:21,337
You cannot.

315
00:20:21,672 --> 00:20:22,997
If you go now,

316
00:20:23,301 --> 00:20:25,406
you will not return alive.

317
00:20:25,912 --> 00:20:27,476
Then on my funeral rite,

318
00:20:29,281 --> 00:20:30,881
light enough incense for me.

319
00:20:30,881 --> 00:20:31,881
General!

320
00:20:31,881 --> 00:20:34,616
I need no signs to show me the path I must take.

321
00:20:34,922 --> 00:20:36,146
I must follow it.

322
00:20:39,351 --> 00:20:40,886
I do not know about the consequences.

323
00:20:41,591 --> 00:20:43,357
Even if you win, General,

324
00:20:45,831 --> 00:20:47,896
you will not win the Princess.

325
00:20:50,402 --> 00:20:51,827
The Princess...

326
00:20:53,101 --> 00:20:54,837
will soon be executed.

327
00:21:08,081 --> 00:21:09,176
I know.

328
00:21:12,591 --> 00:21:14,757
That is why I must fight.

329
00:21:18,061 --> 00:21:20,186
It is the only path left for me.

330
00:22:05,771 --> 00:22:08,476
I wonder if this is too small to build a hut, Mother.

331
00:22:45,051 --> 00:22:46,307
You scoundrels.

332
00:22:49,982 --> 00:22:52,386
You must be here to rob a house when the owner is not home.

333
00:22:52,821 --> 00:22:54,116
Where is On Dal?

334
00:22:54,462 --> 00:22:55,557
On Dal?

335
00:22:55,992 --> 00:22:57,987
Is that the name of the mutt in your yard?

336
00:22:58,762 --> 00:23:00,061
This is my house.

337
00:23:00,061 --> 00:23:01,297
It is your house?

338
00:23:03,061 --> 00:23:05,567
Then reveal your identity.

339
00:23:07,642 --> 00:23:09,767
How dare some petty thieves order me around?

340
00:23:09,771 --> 00:23:10,866
Get him.

341
00:23:52,452 --> 00:23:53,706
Wol Gwang?

342
00:24:00,252 --> 00:24:01,456
Master?

343
00:24:14,742 --> 00:24:15,896
Master?

344
00:24:17,212 --> 00:24:18,366
Master!

345
00:24:22,942 --> 00:24:25,047
Master.

346
00:24:26,652 --> 00:24:28,847
Master.

347
00:25:01,521 --> 00:25:02,716
What are you doing?

348
00:25:03,722 --> 00:25:05,487
I am digging a grave.

349
00:25:06,652 --> 00:25:09,186
- Whose grave? - Of course, it is for my Master.

350
00:25:12,692 --> 00:25:13,926
You died!

351
00:25:14,861 --> 00:25:16,027
Did you not die?

352
00:25:18,002 --> 00:25:20,666
This must be your grave, not mine.

353
00:25:30,242 --> 00:25:31,406
It hurts.

354
00:25:35,482 --> 00:25:37,077
Are you really alive?

355
00:25:38,051 --> 00:25:39,386
You are not a ghost, are you?

356
00:25:39,992 --> 00:25:41,561
I am not a ghost,

357
00:25:41,561 --> 00:25:42,817
but I do feel like a pig.

358
00:25:43,121 --> 00:25:45,732
You definitely had no pulse,

359
00:25:45,732 --> 00:25:47,131
and you were not breathing.

360
00:25:47,131 --> 00:25:49,262
Once you have trained as much as I,

361
00:25:49,262 --> 00:25:51,172
you can last an entire night...

362
00:25:51,172 --> 00:25:53,067
as if you are dead, even though you are alive.

363
00:25:53,732 --> 00:25:54,871
Is that true?

364
00:25:54,871 --> 00:25:56,371
Why are you so curious...

365
00:25:56,371 --> 00:25:58,136
when you are the one who left before learning all I have to teach?

366
00:25:59,341 --> 00:26:00,712
I knew those assassins would only leave once they had fulfilled...

367
00:26:00,712 --> 00:26:02,307
their duty to the last.

368
00:26:02,642 --> 00:26:05,077
So I simply pretended to be dead for a little while.

369
00:26:20,561 --> 00:26:23,926
Were those assassins really sent by the King?

370
00:26:25,101 --> 00:26:26,426
To kill me?

371
00:26:31,041 --> 00:26:32,267
Rest assured.

372
00:26:32,371 --> 00:26:34,341
Now they know you do not live in this house,

373
00:26:34,341 --> 00:26:36,341
and they believe they have killed the owner of the house.

374
00:26:36,341 --> 00:26:37,747
They will not return.

375
00:26:41,381 --> 00:26:43,577
If he has sent assassins after me,

376
00:26:43,992 --> 00:26:46,347
that means something has happened to Ga Jin as well.

377
00:26:47,152 --> 00:26:48,392
What has happened?

378
00:26:48,392 --> 00:26:49,956
You know, do you not?

379
00:26:52,662 --> 00:26:54,057
Why does it matter to you?

380
00:26:54,531 --> 00:26:57,357
You have become a recluse, cutting yourself off from the world.

381
00:26:58,071 --> 00:26:59,666
Please tell me, Master.

382
00:27:05,442 --> 00:27:08,507
The King has imprisoned Ga Jin.

383
00:27:09,281 --> 00:27:10,281
What?

384
00:27:10,281 --> 00:27:12,446
He has become suspicious...

385
00:27:12,752 --> 00:27:14,351
that Ga Jin is plotting treason.

386
00:27:14,351 --> 00:27:16,916
That makes no sense. Why would Ga Jin do that?

387
00:27:17,081 --> 00:27:20,886
Power cannot be split, even between a parent and child.

388
00:27:22,321 --> 00:27:25,757
Furthermore, once a sister who is both wise and skilled...

389
00:27:26,262 --> 00:27:28,327
began to receive the respect of the people,

390
00:27:29,432 --> 00:27:31,327
the King must have become anxious.

391
00:27:32,071 --> 00:27:33,297
So...

392
00:27:33,801 --> 00:27:35,767
what will happen to Ga Jin?

393
00:27:36,142 --> 00:27:38,267
If she cannot prove her innocence,

394
00:27:39,111 --> 00:27:40,706
she will be executed.

395
00:27:45,212 --> 00:27:46,507
This is absurd.

396
00:27:47,851 --> 00:27:50,577
How can she prove her innocence of something she has not done?

397
00:28:00,962 --> 00:28:02,057
Sister.

398
00:28:03,502 --> 00:28:05,926
Do not choose a path that leads to death, when there is one to life.

399
00:28:08,041 --> 00:28:10,166
General On is your sword.

400
00:28:10,942 --> 00:28:13,636
As soon as we recover Adan Fortress...

401
00:28:15,381 --> 00:28:17,547
both you and my brother-in-law will be able to live.

402
00:28:18,081 --> 00:28:19,976
My path to life...

403
00:28:23,821 --> 00:28:26,186
is to die for that person.

404
00:28:28,091 --> 00:28:30,216
Must you be so stubborn?

405
00:28:31,561 --> 00:28:34,257
You can save yourself if you just persuade the General.

406
00:28:37,601 --> 00:28:38,696
Won.

407
00:28:40,871 --> 00:28:42,366
He is someone who became my sword...

408
00:28:43,271 --> 00:28:45,636
and waded through a river of blood.

409
00:28:48,982 --> 00:28:51,206
To satisfy my ambitions,

410
00:28:52,281 --> 00:28:54,216
he continued to wound himself.

411
00:28:57,492 --> 00:28:59,087
At last, he has returned...

412
00:29:00,392 --> 00:29:02,616
to the life he desired.

413
00:29:03,922 --> 00:29:05,027
Therefore,

414
00:29:08,131 --> 00:29:09,797
I am ashamed...

415
00:29:11,172 --> 00:29:12,896
and grateful.

416
00:29:14,601 --> 00:29:15,696
Is that truly...

417
00:29:19,012 --> 00:29:20,537
your dying wish?

418
00:29:24,351 --> 00:29:25,706
My life...

419
00:29:27,252 --> 00:29:29,347
is not under your control.

420
00:29:31,152 --> 00:29:32,247
I have already decided...

421
00:29:34,291 --> 00:29:36,916
to dedicate it to him.

422
00:29:46,031 --> 00:29:47,497
That was a great meal.

423
00:29:47,841 --> 00:29:48,936
Master.

424
00:29:50,271 --> 00:29:51,936
You said it was Adan Fortress?

425
00:29:52,972 --> 00:29:55,277
Does the King wish to have it?

426
00:29:55,781 --> 00:29:57,381
Do not think foolish thoughts.

427
00:29:57,381 --> 00:29:58,381
But Ga Jin...

428
00:29:58,381 --> 00:30:00,476
If you find it difficult to let go,

429
00:30:00,611 --> 00:30:02,317
come to the temple with me.

430
00:30:03,781 --> 00:30:05,646
I have no intention of becoming a monk.

431
00:30:05,892 --> 00:30:07,392
My mother's grave is here as well.

432
00:30:07,392 --> 00:30:09,757
That is all anguish and obsession.

433
00:30:10,222 --> 00:30:13,386
You have not even let go of your mother, much less the Princess.

434
00:30:15,432 --> 00:30:17,626
How must I deal with this fool?

435
00:30:20,631 --> 00:30:21,737
Master.

436
00:30:22,702 --> 00:30:24,136
I have a request.

437
00:30:26,311 --> 00:30:29,337
You want me to find out what situation the Princess is in.

438
00:30:30,012 --> 00:30:31,476
I will not do it. It is too much of a bother.

439
00:30:33,311 --> 00:30:34,416
That is not it.

440
00:30:37,381 --> 00:30:38,847
It is a different request.

441
00:31:55,393 --> 00:31:56,689
Mother.

442
00:32:04,633 --> 00:32:06,029
Are you going?

443
00:32:09,904 --> 00:32:13,068
Have you decided to go?

444
00:32:14,143 --> 00:32:15,368
Yes.

445
00:32:18,514 --> 00:32:21,779
You sure are the biggest fool...

446
00:32:22,283 --> 00:32:24,178
in the whole wide world.

447
00:32:25,354 --> 00:32:28,178
Whom you took in and raised.

448
00:32:31,893 --> 00:32:34,059
I will see you again when I come back...

449
00:32:34,693 --> 00:32:36,389
after seeing Ga Jin.

450
00:32:39,234 --> 00:32:41,299
This is the last time.

451
00:32:46,143 --> 00:32:47,669
Your Highness.

452
00:32:51,113 --> 00:32:53,009
I am grateful...

453
00:32:53,843 --> 00:32:55,708
that a lowly woman like me...

454
00:32:56,313 --> 00:32:59,979
had the honor of looking after you for so many years.

455
00:33:03,123 --> 00:33:07,088
Now go back to the Princess...

456
00:33:08,123 --> 00:33:12,558
and live a long happy life with her.

457
00:33:20,643 --> 00:33:23,368
If you will excuse me now, Your Highness.

458
00:33:29,354 --> 00:33:31,408
Do not call me that.

459
00:33:33,523 --> 00:33:35,919
I will always be your son,

460
00:33:37,993 --> 00:33:40,519
and you will always be my mother.

461
00:33:45,933 --> 00:33:47,859
My dear Dal.

462
00:33:49,004 --> 00:33:50,498
My sweet Dal.

463
00:33:51,743 --> 00:33:53,799
Thank you so much.

464
00:33:55,514 --> 00:33:57,039
Thank you.

465
00:33:58,414 --> 00:33:59,938
Mother.

466
00:34:44,493 --> 00:34:45,819
Dal.

467
00:34:46,863 --> 00:34:48,688
I will see you...

468
00:34:49,664 --> 00:34:50,889
in the next life.

469
00:35:11,854 --> 00:35:13,319
My goodness.

470
00:35:31,073 --> 00:35:32,338
Stop.

471
00:35:38,584 --> 00:35:40,139
You are here, Dal.

472
00:36:05,034 --> 00:36:06,569
I am honored...

473
00:36:10,613 --> 00:36:12,538
to see you again, Princess.

474
00:36:27,894 --> 00:36:30,489
To repay the kindness of Your Majesty,

475
00:36:30,964 --> 00:36:32,658
I, On Dal,

476
00:36:35,604 --> 00:36:38,228
vow to retake Adan Fortress.

477
00:36:59,094 --> 00:37:00,418
Lord Sa.

478
00:37:03,193 --> 00:37:04,389
Lord Sa.

479
00:37:05,133 --> 00:37:07,228
Was the execution carried out?

480
00:37:07,563 --> 00:37:09,798
It was stopped.

481
00:37:12,774 --> 00:37:14,203
What are you talking about?

482
00:37:14,203 --> 00:37:16,269
General On Dal is back.

483
00:37:17,373 --> 00:37:18,879
Dal is back?

484
00:37:19,344 --> 00:37:21,414
What happened to the Princess?

485
00:37:21,414 --> 00:37:22,784
What happened to her?

486
00:37:22,784 --> 00:37:24,809
She was put back in prison.

487
00:37:27,224 --> 00:37:28,823
Let us enter the palace.

488
00:37:28,823 --> 00:37:31,019
Sure. We must. Let us go.

489
00:37:35,164 --> 00:37:36,559
I am so relieved.

490
00:37:37,693 --> 00:37:39,199
Poor Ga Jin.

491
00:37:39,433 --> 00:37:40,699
Therefore,

492
00:37:41,203 --> 00:37:44,769
I humbly ask you to allow me 5,000 troops.

493
00:37:45,743 --> 00:37:47,144
Did you say 5,000?

494
00:37:47,144 --> 00:37:50,343
If I do, are you sure you can retake Adan Fortress?

495
00:37:50,344 --> 00:37:51,869
Yes, Your Majesty.

496
00:37:52,544 --> 00:37:53,838
In addition,

497
00:37:54,844 --> 00:37:58,449
I will retake Gaeripyeong as well as the land west of Jungryeong.

498
00:38:01,883 --> 00:38:03,918
You should not make an empty promise.

499
00:38:04,394 --> 00:38:07,393
I can guess why you returned here...

500
00:38:07,394 --> 00:38:09,329
all of a sudden.

501
00:38:09,794 --> 00:38:12,559
It is out of your desperation to save the Princess,

502
00:38:12,734 --> 00:38:14,699
is it not?

503
00:38:14,734 --> 00:38:16,429
Yes, Your Majesty.

504
00:38:17,734 --> 00:38:20,668
As a man trying to save his wife,

505
00:38:21,844 --> 00:38:23,869
I do not make an empty promise.

506
00:38:24,844 --> 00:38:27,183
It is not acceptable...

507
00:38:27,183 --> 00:38:29,648
to make a promise that cannot be carried out...

508
00:38:30,683 --> 00:38:33,079
just to win His Majesty's favor.

509
00:38:33,584 --> 00:38:35,284
The troops are still exhausted...

510
00:38:35,284 --> 00:38:37,449
from fighting off the Baekje troops.

511
00:38:37,953 --> 00:38:40,023
Daedaero is right.

512
00:38:40,024 --> 00:38:42,294
It will take a while for them to fully recover.

513
00:38:42,294 --> 00:38:44,894
I am sure General On can take care of it.

514
00:38:44,894 --> 00:38:46,759
Silence, all of you.

515
00:38:47,763 --> 00:38:51,429
Given the situation, I can only allow you 3,000 troops.

516
00:38:51,503 --> 00:38:55,239
Can you still retake Adan Fortress?

517
00:38:59,044 --> 00:39:02,309
If you can believe the Princess' innocence and set her free,

518
00:39:03,714 --> 00:39:05,079
I am ready...

519
00:39:06,424 --> 00:39:08,749
to go out and fight.

520
00:39:19,963 --> 00:39:21,229
Dal.

521
00:39:25,174 --> 00:39:26,869
His Majesty has given his permission.

522
00:39:27,404 --> 00:39:28,869
You are free.

523
00:39:30,544 --> 00:39:32,009
Let me take you to Magnolia Hall.

524
00:39:32,144 --> 00:39:33,813
What did you promise him?

525
00:39:33,813 --> 00:39:36,109
Did you promise to retake Adan Fortress?

526
00:39:36,514 --> 00:39:38,614
Is that why His Majesty set me free?

527
00:39:38,614 --> 00:39:41,548
- No, it is not like that. - On Dal.

528
00:39:42,924 --> 00:39:44,389
You did.

529
00:39:45,593 --> 00:39:47,459
You promised that.

530
00:39:48,193 --> 00:39:49,489
Ga Jin.

531
00:39:50,134 --> 00:39:52,499
I am excited to be back in the palace after many years.

532
00:39:53,504 --> 00:39:56,469
I want to eat good food and see some people.

533
00:39:57,233 --> 00:39:58,938
Why did you do that?

534
00:40:00,103 --> 00:40:02,139
You should not have come.

535
00:40:02,343 --> 00:40:03,869
You fool.

536
00:40:04,144 --> 00:40:06,609
Why do you never think about yourself?

537
00:40:09,453 --> 00:40:10,709
Yes, I am...

538
00:40:11,983 --> 00:40:13,678
a fool.

539
00:40:13,823 --> 00:40:15,889
But let us get out of here first.

540
00:40:16,754 --> 00:40:20,259
I hate seeing you locked up like this.

541
00:40:21,093 --> 00:40:23,889
You promised me to go hide in the mountains.

542
00:40:23,894 --> 00:40:26,028
I could not find anywhere to hide.

543
00:40:28,803 --> 00:40:30,428
I had no choice but to come back to you.

544
00:40:35,674 --> 00:40:37,544
Please send General On back.

545
00:40:37,544 --> 00:40:39,883
I will retake Adan Fortress.

546
00:40:39,884 --> 00:40:41,014
Princess.

547
00:40:41,014 --> 00:40:43,048
I would have been executed anyway.

548
00:40:43,614 --> 00:40:45,884
I will give up my life to get the fortress back.

549
00:40:45,884 --> 00:40:47,883
Who says you may step in?

550
00:40:47,884 --> 00:40:49,793
I am the one who received His Majesty's order.

551
00:40:49,794 --> 00:40:51,948
It is not your choice to make.

552
00:40:52,093 --> 00:40:55,119
I will go. Please give the order.

553
00:40:55,223 --> 00:40:58,264
It has already been decided. Please do not take your order back.

554
00:40:58,264 --> 00:40:59,558
Dal.

555
00:41:00,164 --> 00:41:02,099
I said I will go.

556
00:41:07,203 --> 00:41:09,573
