820
00:57:44,904 --> 00:57:48,199
Quiet. If I say it is wild ginseng, then it is wild ginseng.

821
00:57:50,114 --> 00:57:52,909
Wow, look at this.

822
00:57:54,414 --> 00:57:55,638
Here.

823
00:57:57,614 --> 00:57:59,409
Have some wild ginseng and cheer up.

824
00:58:05,293 --> 00:58:07,259
Do not be afraid, Dal.

825
00:58:08,693 --> 00:58:11,358
I am not afraid of anything because I am with you.

826
00:58:11,493 --> 00:58:14,028
Once we retake Adan Fortress tomorrow,

827
00:58:14,834 --> 00:58:17,098
let us leave right away...

828
00:58:17,733 --> 00:58:19,469
after putting Jin and Pung Gae in charge.

829
00:58:20,043 --> 00:58:21,298
I know.

830
00:58:24,074 --> 00:58:25,868
I know that tomorrow...

831
00:58:26,614 --> 00:58:28,538
will be the last time to use my father's sword.

832
00:58:41,023 --> 00:58:43,293
Are you well-prepared for war?

833
00:58:43,293 --> 00:58:47,003
Yes, Your Majesty. We have enough weapons and war horses.

834
00:58:47,003 --> 00:58:49,664
And the soldiers are in high morale.

835
00:58:49,664 --> 00:58:53,499
Once you give us your command, we can set off immediately.

836
00:58:53,904 --> 00:58:56,499
It is different from what I heard.

837
00:58:56,773 --> 00:58:58,043
I heard that...

838
00:58:58,043 --> 00:59:00,644
you cornered them without mercy...

839
00:59:00,644 --> 00:59:03,078
and made them resent you.

840
00:59:03,453 --> 00:59:06,924
You have also killed an officer at the armory.

841
00:59:06,924 --> 00:59:09,179
I must sacrifice the lesser...

842
00:59:09,223 --> 00:59:11,618
for the greater good.

843
00:59:14,394 --> 00:59:17,259
You put great importance on the greater good,

844
00:59:17,993 --> 00:59:20,729
but you are wavered by your personal feelings.

845
00:59:24,933 --> 00:59:26,969
I do not understand.

846
00:59:28,874 --> 00:59:32,808
General Go is deeply...

847
00:59:34,114 --> 00:59:36,679
in love with Princess Pyeonggang.

848
00:59:38,154 --> 00:59:39,713
In love?

849
00:59:39,713 --> 00:59:41,424
General Go is strongly determined...

850
00:59:41,424 --> 00:59:43,594
to destroy Goguryeo...

851
00:59:43,594 --> 00:59:46,719
so that he can have Princess Pyeonggang.

852
00:59:46,763 --> 00:59:49,058
That is his only reason.

853
00:59:50,963 --> 00:59:54,533
You have blessed us with your grace,

854
00:59:54,533 --> 00:59:57,298
and now we are living a decent life.

855
00:59:57,503 --> 00:59:59,904
To repay your kindness,

856
00:59:59,904 --> 01:00:02,899
I am telling you this out of my loyalty to you...

857
01:00:02,973 --> 01:00:06,568
when war is just around the corner.

858
01:00:07,144 --> 01:00:08,909
This is outrageous!

859
01:00:08,914 --> 01:00:10,979
I do not know who told you that,

860
01:00:12,384 --> 01:00:14,618
but I am sure it is a trick to slander me.

861
01:00:16,054 --> 01:00:19,818
Then are you saying...

862
01:00:19,854 --> 01:00:22,689
you have no feelings left for Pyeonggang at all?

863
01:00:28,263 --> 01:00:29,729
When we were young,

864
01:00:31,273 --> 01:00:33,739
I taught her martial arts.

865
01:00:34,703 --> 01:00:35,939
But...

866
01:00:37,314 --> 01:00:40,308
the royal household and my family were deeply ill-fated.

867
01:00:41,983 --> 01:00:44,108
We ended up becoming enemies.

868
01:00:46,513 --> 01:00:49,649
What about the royal wedding that got canceled?

869
01:00:51,193 --> 01:00:54,094
You were a strong candidate as the king's son-in-law,

870
01:00:54,094 --> 01:00:57,888
but Princess Pyeonggang chose On Dal instead.

871
01:00:59,263 --> 01:01:03,098
As a man, you must hold a deep grudge against her.

872
01:01:03,203 --> 01:01:05,374
But you insist that you have no feelings left for her,

873
01:01:05,374 --> 01:01:07,368
so I will believe your words.

874
01:01:07,904 --> 01:01:11,409
But you will not have the authority to command the army.

875
01:01:11,943 --> 01:01:13,273
Your Majesty, that means...

876
01:01:13,273 --> 01:01:17,509
I will entrust you with a more important duty next time.

877
01:01:20,013 --> 01:01:23,788
Then who will command the army?

878
01:01:28,763 --> 01:01:31,288
I will go myself.

879
01:01:32,793 --> 01:01:34,333
It is too dangerous, Your Majesty.

880
01:01:34,334 --> 01:01:36,002
There is someone...

881
01:01:36,003 --> 01:01:38,729
I wish to fight on the battlefield.

882
01:01:39,334 --> 01:01:43,169
That is why I am going to Adan Fortress.

883
01:01:43,203 --> 01:01:45,043
You are going to Adan Fortress?

884
01:01:45,043 --> 01:01:48,739
The soldiers of Goguryeo are coming to attack Adan Fortress.

885
01:01:50,914 --> 01:01:52,249
On Dal...

886
01:01:52,713 --> 01:01:54,949
and Princess Pyeonggang are coming together.

887
01:01:55,824 --> 01:01:57,493
Do you understand it now?

888
01:01:57,493 --> 01:01:59,554
If you want to prove that you have no feelings for the Princess,

889
01:01:59,554 --> 01:02:02,588
you must stay out of this battle.

890
01:02:25,783 --> 01:02:29,219
Why? Are you here...

891
01:02:30,824 --> 01:02:32,649
to see how ruined I am?

892
01:02:32,953 --> 01:02:36,493
You will get another chance.

893
01:02:36,493 --> 01:02:38,388
There is no such thing!

894
01:02:39,394 --> 01:02:41,058
There is no next time.

895
01:02:42,064 --> 01:02:43,459
Do not...

896
01:02:44,574 --> 01:02:46,429
talk to me about chances.

897
01:02:55,814 --> 01:02:57,509
You can yell at me...

898
01:02:58,084 --> 01:02:59,679
and get angry.

899
01:03:02,124 --> 01:03:04,388
I will tolerate everything.

900
01:03:28,513 --> 01:03:31,348
(Adan Fortress)

901
01:03:53,473 --> 01:03:55,499
General On!

902
01:03:57,644 --> 01:04:00,909
General, the advance party tore down the east gate.

903
01:04:02,144 --> 01:04:03,914
Before their main force blocks the gate,

904
01:04:03,914 --> 01:04:05,709
we need to enter the fortress.

905
01:04:09,154 --> 01:04:11,023
Are you here to live?

906
01:04:11,023 --> 01:04:13,094
- We are here to win! - We are here to win!

907
01:04:13,094 --> 01:04:15,924
Are you going to lose and die?

908
01:04:15,924 --> 01:04:18,933
- We will win and live! - We will win and live!

909
01:04:18,933 --> 01:04:21,399
Warriors of Goguryeo.

910
01:04:22,503 --> 01:04:24,328
Let us march forward!

911
01:05:52,594 --> 01:05:54,093
(River Where the Moon Rises)

912
01:05:54,094 --> 01:05:55,094
As a man of Goguryeo,

913
01:05:55,094 --> 01:05:56,663
I cannot abandon the land of Goguryeo.

914
01:05:56,663 --> 01:05:58,264
I am going to fight until the last man standing.

915
01:05:58,264 --> 01:05:59,833
The King of Silla is here to fight himself.

916
01:05:59,833 --> 01:06:01,603
It is meaningless to go on with this fight.

917
01:06:01,603 --> 01:06:02,804
Whether we win or lose,

918
01:06:02,804 --> 01:06:05,129
I must fight until the end. That is my fate as a general.

919
01:06:05,134 --> 01:06:07,002
I know you.

920
01:06:07,003 --> 01:06:09,373
A princess of an empire hid a dagger...

921
01:06:09,373 --> 01:06:11,269
and infiltrated deep into the enemy's camp?

922
01:06:11,313 --> 01:06:13,574
The Princess was captured by the Silla soldiers.

923
01:06:13,574 --> 01:06:16,178
You only think of the Princess even in the end.

924
01:06:16,643 --> 01:06:20,724
Have you loved me at all?

925
01:06:20,724 --> 01:06:22,454
I loved you.

926
01:06:22,454 --> 01:06:25,019
- Dal! - No!

927
01:06:25,154 --> 01:06:26,419
Dal!
